window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>HMS <i>Lion </i>and HMS <i>Unicorn </i>have made it home from their first mission against the alien virus, opening the way for humanity to take the offensive. Now, a major fleet is readying itself to depart into enemy space, intent on smashing the virusâ€™ ability to wage war and destroy the threat once and for all. And Captains Hammond and Campbell will take the lead.</p> <p>But humanity itself is buckling under the strain of endless war. The stresses of fighting are tearing the fleet apart. And a very personal betrayal threatens to plunge the captains and their crews into a bitter feud, deep in alien territory. The stakes could not be higher...and the risk of total defeat has never been so great.</p>"; 
